OL,3,CMan charged after attempt to seriously
OL,4,Cassault police officer
OL,6,FA 53-year-old man has been charged
OL,7,Ffollowing an attempt to seriously
OL,8,Fassault a police officer.
OL,10,FPolice said the incident happened at a
OL,11,Fhospital in Antrim on Friday night.
OL,13,FIt is understood a man attempted to
OL,14,Fstab the police officer with a long,
OL,15,Fsharp item but they narrowly escaped
OL,16,Fserious injury.
OL,18,FThe man is charged with attempted
OL,19,Fgrievous bodily harm with intent,
OL,20,Fassault on police and possession of an
OL,21,Foffensive weapon with attempt.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/2
