OL,3,CMan charged after attempt to seriously
OL,4,Cassault police officer
OL,6,FHe is due to appear before Coleraine
OL,7,FMagistrates' Court on Monday.
OL,9,FIn a statement, the PSNI said: "As is
OL,10,Fusual procedure, all charges will be
OL,11,Freviewed by the Public Prosecution
OL,12,FService."
